{"tid":1733300,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"持久戰同圍城戰，最緊要係補給同補給線","createTime":"2019-11-18T05:28:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T12:01:33.000Z","uid":60740,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3946758576fef80a8b28ad50b3f480ea1e94db24","tid":1733300,"uid":60740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T05:28:36.000Z","msg":"明顯popo係封鎖左poly嘅補給<br />\n但係除左入面嘅人要補給，出面嘅popo都係要補給<br />\n所以依家要嘅唔單單係攻入去救人<br />\n仲要斷佢地補給<br />\n最起碼要斷佢地輪班先<br />\n只要人多，將佢地反包圍好似中大斷補給先<br />\n而我地唔係要完全令popo因為冇補給而走哂<br />\n只要佢地因為斷補給而打開足夠嘅缺口就得，少則可以做我地補給線，大嘅可以走到人<br />\n然後先係諗我地點提供補給比入面嘅手足"},{"pid":"64b077d6d6e41e92275d37f5bab21beeeb051a1c","tid":1733300,"uid":89963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T05:29:41.000Z","msg":"推，咩都試下<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">千祈唔好粟一燒班高官</span></span>"},{"pid":"087b4835d1f93707d7bd184b825507262e800706","tid":1733300,"uid":60740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T05:30:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d52fa3953b8e26c68f6acf42c9513d1c0d1741a8","tid":1733300,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T05:31:38.000Z","msg":"邊有可能斷到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"548644a66801183ee982f6e6a9fae8ab26ea3467","tid":1733300,"uid":279253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T05:31:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />乜都要試 咪撚郁啲高官"},{"pid":"c78e861b8c07b85ef289e2d7cc824a9ebf44777f","tid":1733300,"uid":131122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T05:32:00.000Z","msg":"要機"},{"pid":"e96c257896891d792f3158f8a56d67f5b85d472c","tid":1733